9dBRHrr4bmb2fUu4HLq9zHrxmYDRWQg4I65bprp9zYPaQAES2v-0cHq4U7nwagAQhR4r4aXiNiyPOEAtBT7kHKysKEIialNfITOJIHOjZ2vJlay4uqNMz_AQi5e_gkSS62A86BzUAT3b04JCzkfjgUMHFn-TmkHoA9Veg0MHr5HLsppblKx3y5EcRyG8-yyCUrvPv0Uq2QLVw-Gcl2_TTOgNG-6ZTmkkAmJ1Z60SiuDbB-Tc5o4oYG9aG8rmPFzb4qxsPAQTkmnmCXFlFGlN2AHKUEPVJErruaAPvPkBIKiNSmkl0eU3qHND5lOGsRrV1xcPEB2HECyD4S3PBoIOKFnCEGPfCnw_k4Q/xdYhuGg71DNYljR-pWYsiLGGXZJtaUxm/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="国土安全部将创建自己的航空公司，提供全天候驱逐出境服务"&gt;政府飞机机队的计划，以加强驱逐出境，&lt;/a&gt;作为唐纳德·特朗普反移民运动的一部分。这一消息传出之际，休斯敦民众对政府特工&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/zb2tV1Kq8wBhNuGtl_YydVlcpyPhnl9MIQrsFw4NiWk6Z869kQ0NiKcusQlsa_SklxZAaQrNYEiRgbpvk_FI8JgTJvO7MBCzpS8F2BMKUkyeu-n8R7OSTPnHP0F-21Ts_CIgF9Gdrb_YzTYpUCHCmMoZEzeH1Uswzi-SWJCvFuBhIhXVJ7mwpp1lfcu36ht5jep5i85UeS60cYVk_3Mf-hFY2i_x9v68TATf09r4Bb6kzX9bVlDWSxReptfkQp9nk19RHS96Fw4gt8vChtfkqQGowiAYwgOidw-jUUfZ3pyuvnQWKjFedEwnFJdpHASX5DmKiKzzD46ng4QTjBNe27kxunTKGhlUVlVzv1tymfjvBfLTo4SGiJVt7lq4-zGS5epCU0k/2WYwxWZ6TgFlJQOsGAQrM3I271ERaIqz/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="休斯顿枪击事件造成美国移民扫荡中至少第 8 例死亡"&gt;最近杀害一名手无寸铁的平民的行为&lt;/a&gt;感到愤怒。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;据&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;美联社&lt;/em&gt;报道，在美国生活了 35 年的墨西哥国民洛伦佐·萨尔加多·阿劳霍 (Lorenzo Salgado Araujo) 正与其他男子一起开着一辆面包车去上班，联邦特工拦住了他，他是一位住宅建筑商。虽然特朗普政府声称他&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/umUxLTbh0HY0flWYsJ-_VUO8Bx1ewzGTHEiXQVL1dAC5HJClO7V4S0LcqvySK40ElpWOnIro34_YoRbuVKMUqT_4re1p1HGRSNbqmXOvaHaeOpC23eEV3sgDiR5CtShWgAnk3_N56kR-PX5R2Tj4_12ux13OwhZMyBbZgOPncGrLCizdvsVrnk0b4xltp8qFjZL3XaELpeSVPSf_odTustJZ2tdNVjoLntFqA2oQAYHNIz1BSz21K5V2AX3yNDA-TJp5M6nkAb2Hdq1dvR4Y3KzaemW4Dq34stoc5szBR4N27kLmvs8FtDil4oealrf_TIY-ydJB8to1m-cE0EGTALfP4PUb-s-6bj3WcIjE9OStfHHeQhifMlWofU8/MeZopTJY_MPkTMnwOZDaaRw6F_ck0zst/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="关于一名休斯顿男子被